---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy — SocialProof" noIndex={false}>
  <main style="padding:60px 0 100px;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width:780px;">
      <h1 style="font-size:36px;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="color:var(--text-muted);margin-bottom:48px;">Last updated: January 2025</p>
      <div style="font-size:17px;line-height:1.75;color:#374151;">
        <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">What we collect</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly: name, email address, and testimonial content. We also collect basic usage data (page views, API calls) to operate the service.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">How we use it</h2>
        <p>We use your data to provide the SocialProof service, send transactional emails, and improve the product. We do not sell your data to third parties.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">Data storage</h2>
        <p>Data is stored on Cloudflare infrastructure (D1 database, R2 object storage). Cloudflare's data centers are primarily in the US and EU.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">Your rights</h2>
        <p>You can request a copy of your data or ask us to delete it at any time. Email <a href="mailto:team@socialproof.dev" style="color:var(--brand);">team@socialproof.dev</a>.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use session cookies for authentication. We do not use advertising or tracking cookies.</p>
        <h2 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin:32px 0 12px;">Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Email us at <a href="mailto:team@socialproof.dev" style="color:var(--brand);">team@socialproof.dev</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Base>
